      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――数時間後",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1033.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3330,
          "startTime": 3.33
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "このお仕事も、このお仕事も……\n私には無理ですかね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This job and that job…\nIs it too much for me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、バラエティは無理でも、ライブのMCで\nチャレンジしてみるのはいいですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ even if variety shows are tough‚ trying to challenge myself\nas an MC for live performances is a good idea‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（普段の沙季が「仕事の幅を広げたい」と言ったのなら）\n（もっと希望を通しても良かったんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If Saki usud to say that she wants to \"expand her work opportunities\"）\n（I could have pushed for more options…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今は冷静じゃないからな。失敗は大事だが限度がある）\n（本人や仕事先のためにも、慎重に動かないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But I gotta keepl my cool. While failures are important‚ there are limits.）\n（For Saki and coming jobs‚ I need to act cautiously.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、次は私ですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright‚ it's my turn now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "白石沙季、十八歳。生徒会長やってます！\n好きな食べ物はくさや。よろしくね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Saki Shiraishi‚ 18 years old. I'm the student council president!\nMy favorite food is Kusaya. Nice to meet you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、沙季……！？\nチャレンジって、そういう方向なのか……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Saki…!?\nIs this the kind of challenge you meant…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "え、あの、えっと……皆さん\nどうしてそんなに固まっているんでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um… everyone‚\nwhy are you all frozen like that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、琴乃ちゃん、すずちゃん！？　恐ろしいものを\n見たように目を見開いて、どうしちゃったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kotono-chan‚ Suzu-chan!? Why are your eyes\nlike you've seen something terrifying!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そりゃそうだろう……お客さんも\n引いてるというより、困って笑ってる感じだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I mean… the audience‚ they're more like\nawkwardly laughing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、今のは……くさやが\nダメだったんでしょうか……？　え、違う……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um‚ was what I just said… about kusaya\n… not good…? Wait‚ it's not‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普段ならメンバーがフォローし合うけど……今回は\nあまりに突然だからな。芽衣や渚でさえ苦笑いしてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ the members would support each other‚ but…\nThis was so sudden that even Mei and Nagisa are giving awkward smiles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "え、あ、もう次の曲に行くんですか？\nは、はい、分かりました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ are we moving on to the next song now?\nY-Yes‚ I understand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃と渚に優しく肩を叩かれた……これは辛いな……\nそれにしてもこれは……思った以上にまずいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She got a gentle pat on the shoulder from Kotono and Nagisa… .\nThis is tough…By the way‚ this is… worse than I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 111.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "沙季。……ええと、元気か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki… um‚ how are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "元気ですよ……ふふふ……\n冗談です、心配して下さってありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm feeling fine… Ehehe…\nJust kidding‚ thank you for your concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のライブの後、月ストのみんなにもの凄く\n心配されました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After yesterday's live‚ the Moon Tempest members\nwere really worried about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "妙な空気にしたのは私なのに「何か悩みがあるの？」\n「フォロー出来なくてごめんね」なんて言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I was the one who created that weird atmosphere‚\nthey asked‚ \"Do you have something on your mind?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの優しさが沁みました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and said‚ \"I'm sorry I couldn't support you.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10500,
          "startTime": 151
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そうだ。すみません\nちょっとだけいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their kindness really touched me.\n…Oh‚ right. I'm sorry. Can I ask you something for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　ああ、大丈夫だが……\n誰かに連絡するのか？　やけに神妙な顔をしてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Yeah‚ sure‚ but…\nAre you contacting someone? You look unusually serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 158.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8333.333333299975,
          "startTime": 161.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.333333299981,
          "startTime": 162.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12033.333333299994,
          "startTime": 165.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15566.6666667,
          "startTime": 168.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 169.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のライブの感想を検索しようと思いまして\n皆さんの反応を勉強のためにも知っておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm checking the feedback from yesterday's live performance.\nI need to study the audience's reactions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今から肝試しにでも行きそうな顔だな……\n無理に見なくても……ん、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look like you're about to go on a haunted house…\nYou don't have to force yourself to check it. What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
